.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL_OPEN_CHECK" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-open-check \- check on-chain funds available to open a channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-open-check

.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns confirmed on-chain balance and whether a channel open is feasible.
.PP
Output: JSON object or array from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
